Name: BIAS
Description: ADC buffer bias = 3 and MUX bias = 4 for >440 kS/s.

Name: BW2
Description: RL_A: sel3: 1; sel2: 60; sel1: 16 -> lower cutoff 0.1 Hz

Name: BW3
Description: RL_B: sel3: 0; sel2: 0; sel1L: 17 -> lower cutoff 250 Hz

Name: LOWAB
Description: Select between RL_A and RL_B for each amplifier. Default to RL_A.

Name: STIMENA
Description: Stim enable magic word A. Enabled.

Name: STIMENB
Description: Stim enable magic word B. Enabled.

Name: RECCUR
Description: Charge recovery current limit. sel3: 0; sel2: 0; se11: 9 -> 1uA

Name: LIMREC
Description: Current-lmited charge recovery switch state. Open.
